collection.description:
Olympic Champions 2022.

An exclusive NFT collection dedicated to the XXIV Olympic Winter Games 2022 in Beijing.  

We are a group of crypto-enthusiasts, artists and simply talented people, creating a memorable collection of "Champions" for contemporaries and future generations. 

The cornerstone of our collection is a pioneer, a true champion of innovation in the world - Meta Musk. He is a crazy inventor from a meta universe where something went wrong. Meta Musk has the superpower to build himself into any blockchain network and steal gas. In our reality, he can do a lot of useful and useless things if he is not urgently sent to Mars. NFT with Meta Musk is your key to getting 3 free NFTs, which will be drawn from the real winners of the current Olympic Games, and you will pay only for the gas. The collection consists of 8888 arts. 

The "2022 Olympic Champions" collection of commemorative NFTs will be just 1,000 for 15 sports disciplines. 

Stay tuned for future collections!
collection.name: Olympic Champions 2022
